{"tid":395871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環波霸餐廳欠租 業主收樓追討112萬元","createTime":"2017-09-11T07:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T09:56:48.000Z","uid":33730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80fcdf2a648de26d57dd60c3ef4bb035cf2df7a0","tid":395871,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】位於中環的美國連鎖「波霸餐廳」Hooters Restaurant自今年4月起欠租，遂被業主The Dor Fook Company Limited入稟高院追討，指餐廳違反租約，要求法庭頒發收樓令，並向該間餐廳追討逾112萬港元欠租、利息和賠償。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀透露，雙方於去年3月簽署租約，租用雲咸街43至55號余悅禮行兩個地舖和一樓三個單位，及後於10月份用再租用一樓的另一個單位，首年每月租金合共35.4萬元，並按年增加租金。惟餐廳自今年4月起開始欠租，於是8月發律師信，但餐廳只付部分租金，其餘仍未有理會，遂入稟追討。"},{"pid":"5126cfdff0d94185800f76975d1195bbee58435f","tid":395871,"uid":33730,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/l0MYzeJ2SCl1BC56U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2Fl0MYzeJ2SCl1BC56U.gif&h=dbb0f936&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"678206e674b1111d333cf54676916de5dd48f1c2","tid":395871,"uid":41821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:57:21.000Z","msg":"的確個個波霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8e8f4fe128d63ec40923de495f75249f6de7d9","tid":395871,"uid":22624,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:01:22.000Z","msg":"租霸餐廳"},{"pid":"37bcf6a5baf1562cdea18c601891ec34849e95a9","tid":395871,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:06:53.000Z","msg":"揾港女做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n執硬"},{"pid":"3561edcd0e9ab9b26c23246961c6f862140ba913","tid":395871,"uid":10064,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:20:19.000Z","msg":"係地球最多ipad 既地方搞波霸餐廳<br />\n不如係回教國家開間豬肉bbq 餐廳啦"},{"pid":"b49890a2be2f3896f9ac8b586a7fd57affe1a268","tid":395871,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-